## Case insensitive completion (works)
## works, but I don't understand it, and suspect there are some bad lines here
# Completions
autoload -U compinit
compinit -C
# case-insensitive (all),partial-word and then substring completion
zstyle ':completion:*' matcher-list 'm:{a-zA-Z}={A-Za-z}' \
	    'r:|[._-]=* r:|=*' 'l:|=* r:|=*'

